data.description: This beautiful 2-story home in Castle Rock is waiting for you! Enter into this home that will greet you with soaring ceilings and a fabulous open floor plan perfect for easy entertaining, and family gatherings. Your gourmet kitchen features stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, a massive island, and a walk-in pantry. The primary suite is spacious with an en-suite bathroom featuring dual sinks, a soaking tub, shower, and a walk-in closet. Two more bedrooms are located on the upper level along with another full bathroom, and family room. Enter into your stunning spacious back yard with a large patio, grass, and even a dog run! The oversized garage is perfect for trucks or other toys. This home has everything you need to start making memories with your family.
